35000000.English_Text: Death awaits those who defy the power of the wind!
35000000.Chinese_Text: 违抗风之力的人必将迎接死亡！

35000002.English_Text: This is what the power of wind is like!

35000004.English_Text: I will bind you with the power of lightning.

35000005.English_Text: I will crush you with the power of lightning.

35000011.English_Text: Why don't you just lie down and watch me?

35000012.Original_Text: 으윽……감히 내 제어구를… 니들이 자처 한것이니 후회하지 말아라.
35000012.English_Text: Argh... What did you do to my controlling orb? You'll regret this.
35000012.Chinese_Text: 呃唔…竟敢把我的控制器…都是你们咎由自取，可别后悔了。

35000018.English_Text: This is totally different than before!
35000018.Chinese_Text: 这个感觉！？跟刚才完全不一样！？

35000019.Chinese_Text: 让我们痛快地玩一场吧~

35000020.English_Text: It reminds me of the old days.

35000023.Chinese_Text: 很久没见识这一招吧？寒龙追击！！

35000025.English_Text: Never thought I'd be using all my power!
35000025.Chinese_Text: 没想到我竟然会使出全力！

35000033.Original_Text: 이런 곳을 돌아다니다니.. 넌 악당임이 틀림없군!!
35000033.English_Text: Only a villain would be hanging around a place like this!
35000033.Chinese_Text: 竟然会在这种地方...你果然是坏人！！

35000034.Original_Text: 이 창은 무엇이든 뚫을 수 있지!!

35000035.Original_Text: 이 방패를 뚫을 수는 없을 거다!!

35000040.Chinese_Text: 别以为在远处就可以掉以轻心！！

35000044.Chinese_Text: 竟然露出背后，真不像话

35000051.Chinese_Text: 嘿嘿！你是我的！已经盯上你了

35000052.Original_Text: 가만히 있어! 내가 얼마나 빠른지 보여줄테니 말이야
35000052.English_Text: Wait 'til you see how fast I am!
35000052.Chinese_Text: 别动！让你见识我的速度

35000053.Original_Text: 까꿍~! 무슨 짓 할지 다 알거든?
35000053.Chinese_Text: 哟呵~！我很清楚你要做什么哦？

35000054.Chinese_Text: 弱小的家伙，这么快就倒下了！！

35000056.English_Text: I'm going to kick your butt!

35000058.English_Text: I should have used dual swords...
35000058.Chinese_Text: 咳呵...早知道就用双剑了...

35000060.English_Text: I am as swift as the wind!
35000060.Chinese_Text: 让你见识一下风一样的速度！

35000061.English_Text: My spotlight! Run if you can.
35000061.Chinese_Text: 这是我的舞台~试着逃走吧~！

35000069.English_Text: Hey, slowpoke! Catch me if you can!
35000069.Chinese_Text: 慢吞吞的家伙，试着来抓我吧~！！

35000070.English_Text: Let's take it easy, all right?

35000073.English_Text: What? When did you get there?

35000075.Chinese_Text: 竟然躲开了我的攻击，不错嘛

35000077.English_Text: I'll help you wrap it up.

35000078.English_Text: You're too weak to begin with...

35000094.English_Text: Let's get this show on the road!
35000094.Chinese_Text: 很好...来痛快地玩一下吧！！

35000098.Original_Text: 여기선 내가 원하는 걸 찾을 수 있겠군..
35000098.English_Text: I may find what I'm looking for here...

35000099.Chinese_Text: 让你明白我们之间的差距！

35000101.English_Text: There is only one way: down!

35000102.English_Text: It's not going to be easy.

35000105.Chinese_Text: 什么，怎么回事！模样改变了！！

35000106.English_Text: How about we catch our breath first?

35000108.English_Text: There's no place my axe can't reach!

35000109.English_Text: It's about time to end this.

35000113.English_Text: Krrrr! I'll wipe you all out!

35000115.English_Text: I can't take this no more!

35000119.English_Text: Let's get this show on the road!
35000119.Chinese_Text: 很好...来痛快地玩一下吧！！

35000120.Chinese_Text: 让你见识一下...我的全力！！

35000122.English_Text: Let's call it a day here.

35000128.English_Text: It's not going to be easy.

35000131.English_Text: I feel a strong power... Show your sword!
35000131.Chinese_Text: 感受到强大的力量...亮剑吧！

35000135.Chinese_Text: 来做个了结...堵上一切决一胜负吧！

35000136.Original_Text: 도망칠 수 있을 거라 생각치 마라!
35000136.English_Text: You can't run away from me!

35000140.Original_Text: 이... 이건 도망이 아닌 작전상 후퇴다!
35000140.Chinese_Text: 这...这不是逃走，而是战略撤退！

35000141.Chinese_Text: 竟然是洪梅花...没办法，快逃走~！

35000142.Original_Text: 강한 자를 찾고 있었다, 드디어 나타났군.
35000142.Chinese_Text: 我一直在寻找强者，今天终于等到了。

35000143.Original_Text: 자, 실력 한 번 확인해 볼까?
35000143.English_Text: All right, let's see what you've got.
35000143.Chinese_Text: 来，让我看看你的实力吧！

35000144.Chinese_Text: 真...真是了不起的实力...呃唔...

35000145.Chinese_Text: 没必要的存在们...全都给我消灭吧！

35000146.Original_Text: 네 녀석 따위에게 낭비할 시간은 없다!
35000146.English_Text: I ain't got no time to waste on you!
35000146.Chinese_Text: 我没有时间浪费在你身上！

35000148.Chinese_Text: 竟然输给这种程度...气死我也...

35000149.English_Text: Time for the real fight now!

35000151.Chinese_Text: 强攻击：我绝不会屈服于邪恶！！

35000152.Chinese_Text: 死亡时：我的冒险还未结束...

35000153.English_Text: We meet again... I'm stronger now.
35000153.Chinese_Text: 战斗开始时：又见面了...这次不会像上次一样！

35000154.Chinese_Text: 强攻击：在那之后，我付出了巨大努力！

35000155.Chinese_Text: 盾牌猛击：为了消灭邪恶，我变得更加强大！

35000156.Chinese_Text: 战斗结束时：苦难越多，我越强大。

35000157.Chinese_Text: 战斗开始时：到了结束这一切的时候...

35000158.Chinese_Text: 盾牌格挡：有本事就来刺穿吧！！

35000160.Chinese_Text: 跳跃劈击：在这场战斗赌上我的一切！！

35000161.English_Text: I'll show you how I break my limits!

35000162.Chinese_Text: 这是一场没有遗憾的战斗...

35000163.Chinese_Text: 【丧失控制权】开始消除威胁因素。

35000164.English_Text: [Caution] Divine Power overflow. 50% remaining before overload
35000164.Chinese_Text: 【注意】过度输出神力。超载进行率50%。

35000165.English_Text: [Warning] Divine Power overflow. 80% remaining before overload
35000165.Chinese_Text: [警告]过度输出神力。超载进行率80%。

35000166.Original_Text: [위험] 과부하 상태 진입. 과출력 신력 소모 진행
35000166.Chinese_Text: [危险]进入超载状态。开始消耗过度输出的神力。

35000167.English_Text: Who dares to challenge the power of lightning?

35000169.Chinese_Text: 竟然能击倒我，真了不起。

35000170.English_Text: Challenging the king of the wind? Preposterous!
35000170.Chinese_Text: 竟敢挑战风之帝王，真是可笑！

35000173.English_Text: The treasure here is all mine!
35000173.Chinese_Text: 这里的宝物全都是我的！

35000174.English_Text: Are you after the treasure as well?

35000176.English_Text: My power reverberates through the mountains!

35000177.English_Text: Run for your lives... You weak losers!
35000177.Chinese_Text: 逃走吧，弱小的蝼蚁们，哈哈哈…

35000181.Dev_Desc: 낙원대성 - 이곳은 나의 무대! 모두, 즐길 준비는 되어있나?
35000181.Original_Text: 이곳은 나의 무대! 모두, 즐길 준비는 되어있나?
35000181.English_Text: This is my spotlight! Are you ready to party?
35000181.Chinese_Text: 这里是我的舞台！都来享乐吧！

35000183.English_Text: Who dares to challenge the power of lightning?

35000189.English_Text: Challenging the king of the wind? Preposterous!
35000189.Chinese_Text: 竟敢挑战风之帝王，真是可笑！

35000199.English_Text: I can't be defeated by a peace of meat...

35000202.English_Text: It is me, to the rescue!

35000206.Chinese_Text: 久违的战斗，真是令人想念。

35000209.English_Text: Get ready for the final touch.

35000213.English_Text: Stay right there. That's your grave.

35000214.English_Text: This is the power of wind.

35000219.English_Text: Now that's what I call a storm.

35000220.Chinese_Text: 你有什么办法对付这阵风？

35000221.English_Text: I should take it up a notch.

35000225.English_Text: I haven't used all my power yet!

35000230.English_Text: Challenging the king of the wind? Preposterous!
35000230.Chinese_Text: 竟敢挑战风之帝王，真是可笑！

35000235.English_Text: What should I do with this wind?
35000235.Chinese_Text: 你有什么办法对付这阵风？

35000238.English_Text: Who dares to challenge the power of lightning?

35000240.English_Text: Face the wrath of the sky!
35000240.Chinese_Text: 苍空之愤怒将笼罩你们！

35000243.English_Text: No more joking around. Get lost!
35000243.Chinese_Text: 玩笑就开到这里...快回去吧！

35000244.Original_Text: 뭐야? 너도 나의 장난감을 뺏으러 온 거야??
35000244.English_Text: Are you also here to steal my toy?
35000244.Chinese_Text: 什么？你也来抢我的玩具？

35000246.English_Text: Hacho told me to protect the Halfmoon Herb!

35000248.Chinese_Text: 攻击时一定要全神贯注！

35000249.Original_Text: 제대로 하는 거 맞아? 왜 그때처럼 안되는 거지?
35000249.English_Text: Are you doing this right? Why is it not working this time?
35000249.Chinese_Text: 这真的没错吗？为什么不像上次一样？

35000250.Chinese_Text: 等，等一下...这样下去不行。

35000253.English_Text: Come on! Up on your feet!

35000255.Original_Text: 하찮은 것들! 네놈들이 내 상대가 될 것 같으냐!!
35000255.English_Text: You are no match for me!
35000255.Chinese_Text: 一群废物！你们以为能打败我？！

35000258.English_Text: You're as good as a dead body!
35000258.Chinese_Text: 我这就让你们命赴黄泉！

35000259.Original_Text: 도무지 이해 안 가는 것들 투성이야
35000259.Chinese_Text: 真是一堆让人搞不明白的事情。

35000261.English_Text: How dare you enter our territory!

35000263.Original_Text: 너의 힘을 흡수하면, 난 얼마나 더 강해질까? 크크…
35000263.English_Text: I will make your power mine... Haha!
35000263.Chinese_Text: 若吸收你的力量，我会变得多强呢？呵呵...

35000264.Original_Text: 크크크... 살살 다뤄줄테니 어디 한번 받아봐랏!
35000264.English_Text: Let's see if you can take this!
35000264.Chinese_Text: 呵呵呵...我会手下留情，接招吧！

35000265.Original_Text: 흥! 시시하군… 유흥은 끝났다. 이만 끝내주도록 하지!
35000265.Chinese_Text: 哼！真是无聊...余兴节目到此为止。结束这一切吧！

35000267.Original_Text: 넌 그저 내게 필요한 재물일뿐이야 크크크…
35000267.English_Text: You're nothing but a mere sacrifice!
35000267.Chinese_Text: 你只是我需要的祭品而已，呵呵呵...

35000269.English_Text: I can see what you're up to!

35000270.Chinese_Text: 让你见识狂风骤雨般的攻击~！

35000273.English_Text: Trying to steal from a pirate?

35000274.English_Text: Hacho will be furious if we let them go!
35000274.Chinese_Text: 放走他们会被夏草责骂！！

35000276.Chinese_Text: 我们保护的竟然是这种家伙...

35000278.Original_Text: 날 원망하지 마, 시키는 대로 할 뿐이니까
35000278.English_Text: I only do what I am told to do.
35000278.Chinese_Text: 不要埋怨我，我只是奉命行事。

35000279.English_Text: I also don't want to do this...

35000283.Original_Text: 제법이군, 내 밑으로 올 생각 없나?
35000283.English_Text: How about you work for me?
35000283.Chinese_Text: 实力不错，想不想加入我的麾下？

35000284.English_Text: I'll forgive you if you step back now.
35000284.Chinese_Text: 妨碍者...若现在离开，我还可以网开一面。

35000291.English_Text: You told everyone that I'm constipated!?
35000291.Chinese_Text: 什么？！把我便秘的事情说出去的是你？？！

35000292.Original_Text: 그래그래! 나의 손에 죽는 것만큼 큰 선물은 없지!
35000292.English_Text: I give you an honorable death, by me!
35000292.Chinese_Text: 很好，很好！没有比死在我手中更好的礼物！

35000294.Chinese_Text: 让我看看，你到底隐瞒着什么！

35000295.Chinese_Text: 我就是天下无敌的石拳大人！！

35000298.English_Text: This is the punch of truth! Haha!
35000298.Chinese_Text: 这就是100%真实的拳头！！哇哈哈！

35000299.Original_Text: 뭔가 숨기는 게 있는 것 같은데?

35000302.Original_Text: 뭐 우리야 시킨 거만 잘하면 되지..
35000302.English_Text: We do what we're asked to do...

35000303.English_Text: I was told to do this...

35000305.English_Text: Bind this one who attacked the leader!
35000305.Chinese_Text: 就是这家伙侮辱了门主大人！绑了！

35000315.English_Text: Bare the wrath of the Blue Bandits!

35000318.English_Text: A Blueskin's arrow never misses the target.

35000325.English_Text: I'll slash you to pieces like it's nothing.

35000342.English_Text: Want a piece of my weapon?

35000344.English_Text: I won't go easy on you!

35000355.English_Text: Will this club be enough punishment?
35000355.Chinese_Text: 知道被棍棒殴打会变怎么样吗？

35000357.English_Text: Ready or not, here I come!
35000357.Chinese_Text: 给我藏好了...可不要被发现哦！

35000359.English_Text: Where're you going? Take me with you!

35000361.English_Text: Play with me, play with me, play with me...
35000361.Chinese_Text: 一起玩...一起玩...一起玩...一起玩...

35000367.Dev_Desc: 잿빛 어둑시니_덩치_전투시작_2_이걸로 때리면 재밌는 소리가 나
35000367.English_Text: This weapon makes an interesting sound.
35000367.Chinese_Text: 用这个敲打会发出有趣的声音

35000381.English_Text: Bare the wrath of the Sura!
35000381.Chinese_Text: 见识那位大人的力量吧

35000383.English_Text: This is how it's going to be!

35000387.English_Text: Each shot will bring you closer to death!
35000387.Chinese_Text: 让你见识每一箭的恐惧

35000391.English_Text: I'll make you regret coming here!
35000391.Chinese_Text: 真是不怕死，竟敢来这里

35000393.English_Text: I'm killing you on behalf of the Sura!

35000397.English_Text: Get a taste of my power!

35000405.English_Text: It won't be easy this time!

35000425.English_Text: Where should I hit you first?

35000427.English_Text: My blade is thirsty for blood.

35000428.English_Text: It might hurt just a little.

35000429.Chinese_Text: 我比你想象中更残忍哦？

35000432.English_Text: Let us prove this to you!

35000435.English_Text: What a perfect day to die.

35000441.English_Text: It didn't even make me blink!

35000443.English_Text: This is the sword of the Sole Star!

35000445.English_Text: My arrows never miss a target.

35000450.English_Text: One arrow is all I need.

35000452.English_Text: This goes right to your head!

35000455.English_Text: All it takes is a single arrow!

35000463.English_Text: This calls for some extra money!

35000468.Dev_Desc: 푸른손 하초_전투시작_1_너냐? 내 동료들을 죽인 게!
35000468.English_Text: Was it you? The one who killed my friends?
35000468.Chinese_Text: 是你吗？杀死我同伴的混蛋！

35000469.English_Text: You daring me must be a joke...
35000469.Chinese_Text: 毛头小子不知天高地厚...

35000474.Dev_Desc: 와륜_전투시작_2_감히 내게 대적하고 무사할 것 같나?
35000474.Original_Text: 감히 내게 대적하고 무사할 것 같나?
35000474.English_Text: Walk out alive after provoking me? Not a chance.
35000474.Chinese_Text: 你以为跟我战斗还会平安无事？

35000478.Dev_Desc:
적혈두건_운반해_전투시작_1_웬 소란이냐!
네 놈은 또 뭐냐!?
35000478.English_Text:
What's the fuss?
Who are you?!
35000478.Chinese_Text:
谁在引发骚乱！
你这家伙又是谁？！

35000479.English_Text: Did the Plum Blossom send you?

35000480.English_Text: You want to work for me?

35000481.English_Text: Hey! Let's talk it out first.

35000483.Chinese_Text: 没必要的存在们…全都给我消灭吧！

35000485.Dev_Desc: 환영홍매화_전투시작_3_네 녀석 따위에게 낭비할 시간은 없다!
35000485.Original_Text: 네 녀석 따위에게 낭비할 시간은 없다!
35000485.English_Text: I ain't got no time to waste on you!
35000485.Chinese_Text: 我没有时间浪费在你身上！

35000490.English_Text: What's your first impression of me?

35000496.Dev_Desc: 해수_외로운 어둠_스킬사용_1_편하게 있어! 내가 안아 줄게
35000496.English_Text: Relax. I'll make you more comfortable.

35000501.English_Text: Get a taste of my power!

35000502.Dev_Desc: 대지를 거니는 자 벌판 위의 왕_전투시작_1_나는 대지를 거니는 자

35000503.Dev_Desc: 대지를 거니는 자 벌판 위의 왕_전투시작_2_내가 벌판 위의 왕이다!
35000503.English_Text: I'm the king of the plain!

35000504.Dev_Desc: 대지를 거니는 자 벌판 위의 왕_전투시작_3_이곳에선 내가 가장 강하다!
35000504.English_Text: I am the king around here!

35000505.Dev_Desc: 대지를 거니는 자 벌판 위의 왕_전투시작_4_넓은 벌판을 보거라

35000506.Dev_Desc: 대지를 거니는 자 벌판 위의 왕_스킬사용_1_꽤나 아플 것이다

35000507.Dev_Desc: 먼저 올라선 자 대들보 위의 왕_전투시작_1_누가 나를 깨우는가?

35000508.Dev_Desc: 먼저 올라선 자 대들보 위의 왕_전투시작_2_내가 대들보 위의 왕이다
35000508.English_Text: I'm the King Above the Girders.

35000509.Dev_Desc: 먼저 올라선 자 대들보 위의 왕_전투시작_3_이곳에선 내가 가장 강하다!
35000509.English_Text: I am the king around here!

35000510.Dev_Desc: 먼저 올라선 자 대들보 위의 왕_전투시작_4_내가 가장 먼저 올라왔지

35000511.Dev_Desc: 먼저 올라선 자 대들보 위의 왕_스킬사용_1_자, 이 힘을 받아봐라!

35000512.Dev_Desc: 바다에서 태어난 자 해변의 왕_전투시작_1_이곳은 내가 태어난 곳..
35000512.English_Text: This is where I was born...

35000513.Dev_Desc: 바다에서 태어난 자 해변의 왕_전투시작_2_나는 이곳의 왕이다!
35000513.English_Text: I'm the king of this place!

35000514.Dev_Desc: 바다에서 태어난 자 해변의 왕_전투시작_3_이곳에선 내가 가장 강하다!
35000514.English_Text: I am the king around here!

35000515.Dev_Desc: 바다에서 태어난 자 해변의 왕_전투시작_4_내 밑으로 오겠다고?
35000515.English_Text: You want to work for me?

35000516.Dev_Desc: 바다에서 태어난 자 해변의 왕_스킬사용_1_특별히 보여주지!

35000519.English_Text: Let's see how fast you can go!

35000521.English_Text: Watch it! Here come some pine cones!
35000521.Chinese_Text: 小心眼睛！松球飞过去啦！！

35000525.English_Text: I'm going to pierce right through you!

35000527.English_Text: This is going to be interesting!

35000528.English_Text: You look strong. Come at me!
35000528.Chinese_Text: 你看起来很强...来战斗吧！

35000534.English_Text: I'll chop you like a piece of meat!

35000539.English_Text: Feel the pain we've been feeling...

35000545.English_Text: Are you messing with me? I'm real mad!

35000547.English_Text: I'm gonna stick it to ya!

35000550.English_Text: Don't let Ape King Ogong know about this fight!
35000550.Chinese_Text: 这场胜负不能让乐猿大圣知道！

35000552.English_Text: Are you also trying to chase me away?

35000554.Original_Text: 너도 내 검은 털이 마음에 안 드는 거냐!
35000554.English_Text: Do you have a problem with me?

35000555.English_Text: I'll show you what I'm made of!

35000566.Chinese_Text: 把口袋里的东西全都交出来！！

35000586.English_Text: I won't go easy on you!

35000588.English_Text: Your fist feels like a feather to me.

35000590.Chinese_Text: 你要为自己的行动付出代价

35000593.English_Text: You should have just kept walking.

35000598.English_Text: You must be out of your mind.

35000603.English_Text: Do you want to taste pain?
35000603.Chinese_Text: 想尝一尝痛苦的滋味吗.

35000604.English_Text: Shall I show you what pain is?

35000605.Chinese_Text: 让你后悔没有走过这里。

35000610.Chinese_Text: 让你后悔进入我们的地盘！

35000614.English_Text: Pain is what I can offer.

35000617.English_Text: You're not supposed to be here...

35000623.English_Text: Here comes the next round of pain.

35000625.English_Text: You shouldn't have set foot here.

35000626.English_Text: I can't let you leave alive.

35000627.Chinese_Text: 我会然你后悔来到这里。

35000628.English_Text: No one's allowed to take what's mine.

35000629.English_Text: This how you use a bow.

35000635.English_Text: This blow will end it all.

35000636.English_Text: We must now engage in fisticuffs!

35000637.English_Text: I do believe this will be quite painful.

35000638.English_Text: I rather do enjoy a good fight!

35000641.English_Text: This is certainly a good bit of fun!

35000642.English_Text: It seems you fancy a bit of fun.

35000643.English_Text: This duel is as sweet as carrot juice!

35000645.English_Text: It seems I'm in a predicament!

35000651.English_Text: I happen to be as swift as a hare!

35000655.English_Text: Oh dear... This will sting a bit.

35000657.English_Text: This may come as a shock!

35000685.English_Text: I'll show you what power is...

35000690.English_Text: I want to see you bleed...

35000691.English_Text: Killing is always so much fun...

35000695.English_Text: I love to hear people screaming...

35000696.English_Text: Which weapon should I use to slay you with...?

35000704.English_Text: Hey! So good to see you here!

35000705.English_Text: You found your way here, too!

35000707.English_Text: Oh. I'm surprised to see you here.

35000710.Original_Text: 오! 이런 데서 만날 줄 몰랐는데?
35000710.Chinese_Text: 哦!没想到会在这种地方见面.

35000711.Original_Text: 왠지 오늘은 널 만날 거 같더라~
35000711.English_Text: I had a feeling that I'd run into you today.

35000712.Chinese_Text: 我还以为是谁呢果然是你啊?

35000714.English_Text: Let's see how strong you are now!
35000714.Chinese_Text: 我们比一比到底强大了多少?

35000715.Original_Text: 오랜만에 실력 한번 볼까? 어디 한번 덤벼봐!
35000715.Chinese_Text: 好久没看你的实力了.来挑战一下吧!

35000716.English_Text: Let's duel for old time's sake!
35000716.Chinese_Text: 在这种意义上久违的对联怎么样.

35000717.English_Text: How about a match? You and me!

35000718.Original_Text: 이럴 게 아니라 실력 한번 확인해 보자!
35000718.English_Text: I should see how strong you are!
35000718.Chinese_Text: 不是这样的我们来确认一下实力吧!

35000719.English_Text: I want to see your skills!
35000719.Chinese_Text: 我们来测试一下变得有多强大吧?

35000720.Original_Text: 마지막 시련으로 나와 겨뤄보는 건 어때?
35000720.English_Text: How about a duel with me to end this ordeal?
35000720.Chinese_Text: 用最后的考验和我较量怎么样?

35000721.English_Text: We can still have fun without an audience, right?
35000721.Chinese_Text: 虽然没有观众但是久违的玩一次吧?

35000722.Chinese_Text: 为了热身要不要打一架?

35000723.Original_Text: 아직 나를 뛰어넘을 순 없을 걸? 간만에 대련이다!
35000723.English_Text: You can't get past me! Just try it!
35000723.Chinese_Text: 还不能超越我吧?好久没对联了!

35000726.English_Text: Avoid this? Has it increased a lot?
35000726.Chinese_Text: 躲著这个.进步了很多啊?

35000729.Chinese_Text: 好好看看寒气是怎么扩散的!

35000730.English_Text: You know how to break it!

35000733.English_Text: Um... Shall I try my best?

35000734.English_Text: I still need to get stronger~

35000735.English_Text: Dare you on the subject of a weak servant!
35000735.Chinese_Text: 你这个弱小的奴婢竟敢.

35000736.English_Text: I'll show you the power of the bloodbath!
35000736.Chinese_Text: 给我看看血雨牌的力量!

35000747.English_Text: If you practice a little more, you will become strong soon?
35000747.Chinese_Text: 再修炼一点的话、马上就会变强吧?

35000748.Chinese_Text: 像这样偶尔练习一下吧~

35000751.English_Text: Do you want to level up a bit?

35000753.English_Text: If it's not a coincidence, can you stop it?
35000753.Chinese_Text: 如果不是偶然的话应该可以阻止吧?

35000754.Chinese_Text: 太好了.请不要失去刚才的感觉.

35000755.Original_Text: 때론 막기 힘든 강한 공격도 있습니다.
35000755.English_Text: Sometimes there are strong attacks that are difficult to block.
35000755.Chinese_Text: 有时也有很难阻止的强烈攻击.

35000756.English_Text: I'll show you one more time.

35000758.Original_Text: 잘 피하셨습니다. 큰 공격 뒤엔 허점이 생깁니다.
35000758.English_Text: You did well. After a big attack, you have a loophole.
35000758.Chinese_Text: 您躲开了.大攻击后会出现漏洞.

35000759.Original_Text: 숨겨둔 비기가 있다면, 이때 사용하면 좋습니다.
35000759.English_Text: If you have a hidden secret, this is a good time to use it.
35000759.Chinese_Text: 如果有隐藏的秘籍，这时使用比较好.

35000760.Original_Text: 아무도 날 신경쓰지 않는군.. 내 힘을 보여주지!!
35000760.English_Text: No one cares about me... I'll show you my power!!
35000760.Chinese_Text: 谁都不关心我…展示我的力量！！

35000761.English_Text: Gather the power of thunder.. I will punish you!!
35000761.Chinese_Text: 聚集雷电的力量.。我会惩罚你的！！

35000762.English_Text: Ugh... I'm tired after I've used my strength...
35000762.Chinese_Text: 咳呃…费了不少力气、累了…

35000765.English_Text: Power of lightning... accept my call!
35000765.Chinese_Text: 闪电的力量啊…接受我的召唤吧！

35000766.English_Text: By the power of the wind!

35000771.English_Text: Cute children.. I will punish you soon!
35000771.Chinese_Text: “可爱的孩子们……我会惩罚你们的！”

35000773.English_Text: Don't show me the new born me!!

35000774.English_Text: I'll show you the ultimate stab!

35000775.English_Text: I am angry. I will curse you guys..

35000776.English_Text: Do you want new powers too?

35000778.English_Text: It won't be easy this time.

35000780.English_Text: If this is all... I will die.

35000792.English_Text: It's the price you paid for making me angry!!

35000797.English_Text: This will be different! Yeon~! Kwon Wa Gwangpo!

35000798.English_Text: I'm going to wipe it all out! Jin~Sal! Kwon and Gwangpo!

35000800.Original_Text: 멀리 있어도 제 검기는 피할 수 없을 겁니다.
35000800.English_Text: “Even if you are far away, you will not be able to avoid my sword.”
35000800.Chinese_Text: “就算距离很远，也无法避开我的剑。”

35000801.Original_Text: 이야~ 여기까지 올라온 게 운은 아니시군요
35000801.English_Text: Hey, you're not lucky to have come this far.
35000801.Chinese_Text: “喂，你能走到这一步，倒是不走运。”

35000803.English_Text: Then shall we raise the tempo one more?

35000804.English_Text: From now on, I will go with all my power!!

35000807.English_Text: It's going to be tough this time.

35000810.English_Text: Fly like a butterfly... like a bee!

35000811.English_Text: I just came out because Kogondae-nim pushed me out..
35000811.Chinese_Text: “我出来是因为高权台尼姆把我赶出去了……”

35000812.English_Text: Aigoo Sohyup! Kogondae-nim also avoids this much.
35000812.Chinese_Text: “爱吾苏赫！功德尼姆也避而远之。”

35000813.English_Text: “Actually, I’ve been warming up so far.”

35000814.English_Text: If you can't stop it, it's going to be a disaster!
35000814.Chinese_Text: “如果你不能阻止它，那将是一场灾难！”

35000815.English_Text: “There used to be, but not anymore.”

35000816.Original_Text: 우와 이거 제대로 하지 않으면 안되겠는데요?
35000816.English_Text: Wow, I don't have to do this right?

35000817.English_Text: I'm weak. So please be gentle.

35000818.Original_Text: 빨리 끝내고 청주 한 잔하러 가죠!
35000818.English_Text: Let's finish it quickly and go get a glass of sake!

35000820.English_Text: Oh, let's take a break and do it! Yes?

35000821.Original_Text: 자네가 내 상대인가? 정정당당한 승부를 겨뤄보자!
35000821.English_Text: Are you my opponent? Let's compete fairly!

35000822.English_Text: A stab is the most honest attack!

35000824.English_Text: I will fight with all my might!

35000826.English_Text: I'll bet on the pride of a warrior!

35000827.Original_Text: 내 혼을 담은 극한의 찌르기를 보여주지!
35000827.English_Text: I'll show you the extreme stabs that contain my soul!
35000827.Chinese_Text: “我给你看看，蕴含我灵魂的极刺！”

35000829.Original_Text: 기회는 많았던 거 같은데, 이제 끝낼 시간입니다!
35000829.English_Text: Looks like you've had a lot of opportunities, now it's time to end it!
35000829.Chinese_Text: “看来你的机会很多，现在该结束了！”

35000830.English_Text: I wanted to fight with Sohyup once!

35000836.English_Text: Are you disappointed that you still can't avoid this?
35000836.Chinese_Text: “你对自己还是无法避免这件事感到失望吗？”

35000837.English_Text: “If you are vigilant, you will become like Kogondae.”
35000837.Chinese_Text: “如果你保持警惕，你就会变得像空权台一样。”

35000838.Original_Text: 소협, 우리 그냥 대충 시간때우는건 어때요?
35000838.English_Text: Sohyup, how about we just pass the time?

35000839.English_Text: Hey, are you coming out like this?

35000840.English_Text: A break is also a strategy!

35000844.Dev_Desc: 달빛바람_반달비무제 대사(연속사격) - 이것도 한 번 막아 보시지!?
35000844.English_Text: Would you like to stop this too!?

35000845.English_Text: It's pretty good? How about this?

35000850.English_Text: Um... If I do this, will I win?

35000852.English_Text: You'll figure it out right away!

35000884.English_Text: Weak guys.. Who dare you challenge!!

35000892.English_Text: This power... is it up to here?

35000894.English_Text: You fools, the dawn is already bright...

35000896.English_Text: All you have left is death!

35000899.English_Text: The shadow of doom will destroy everything!

35000900.English_Text: Don't blow me away without a trace!

35000901.English_Text: Khahahaha! I can smell the treasure here.
35000901.Chinese_Text: 哈哈哈哈！我在这里都能闻到宝物的味道。

35000902.English_Text: I've found almost all of them...

35000903.English_Text: The treasure belongs to me.. Oh no, it's my enemy!!
35000903.Chinese_Text: 宝物是我的……哦不，是我的敌人！！

35000904.Original_Text: 크하하하! 들켜 버렸군. 그래도 보물은 내것이다!
35000904.English_Text: Khahahaha! You've been caught. But the treasure is mine!
35000904.Chinese_Text: 哈哈哈哈！你被抓到了，宝物是我的！

35000906.English_Text: Cute little bastards! I'll turn you to dust!
35000906.Chinese_Text: 可爱的小混蛋！我要把你变成尘土！

35000907.Original_Text: 네놈들은 위대한 수라 재림의 거름이 될 것이다!
35000907.English_Text: You guys will be the manure for the great Sura Second Coming!
35000907.Chinese_Text: 你们将成为伟大的苏拉第二次降临的肥料！

35000908.Dev_Desc: 대지를 두드리는자 불모지의 왕_전투시작_1_나는 대지를 두드리는 자
35000908.English_Text: I am the one who knocks on the earth

35000909.Dev_Desc: 대지를 두드리는자 불모지의 왕_전투시작_2_내 허락없인 아무것도 할 수 없다!
35000909.Original_Text: 내 허락없인 아무것도 할 수 없다!
35000909.English_Text: You can't do anything without my permission!
35000909.Chinese_Text: 没有我的允许，你什么都不能做！

35000910.Dev_Desc: 대지를 두드리는자 불모지의 왕_전투시작_3_이곳은 모두 내 지배 하에 있다!
35000910.Original_Text: 이곳은 모두 내 지배 하에 있다!
35000910.English_Text: This place is all under my control!
35000910.Chinese_Text: 这里，一切都在我的掌控之中！

35000911.Dev_Desc: 대지를 두드리는자 불모지의 왕_전투시작_4_거칠고 메마른 땅의 힘을 느껴봐라
35000911.English_Text: Feel the power of the rough and dry land
35000911.Chinese_Text: 感受粗糙和干燥土地的力量

35000914.Dev_Desc: 풍신_바람의 힘에 저항하는 자여.. 그 대가를 치르게 해주마.
35000914.Original_Text: 바람의 힘에 저항하는 자여.. 그 대가를 치르게 해주마.
35000914.English_Text: You who resist the power of the wind... I will pay the price.
35000914.Chinese_Text: 你们这些抗拒风之力的人……我会付出代价的。

35000915.English_Text: The wind is always around you!!

35000919.English_Text: Blood is boiling, show me more!

35000921.English_Text: The end of those who cried a lie!
35000921.Chinese_Text: 那些哭着说谎的人的结局！

35000926.English_Text: The wind doesn't die... it just disappears...

35000927.Dev_Desc: 1인 던전 동충 - 돌풍의 눈 이후 횡이동 시 - 나의 힘을 보았느냐? 크하하하!
35000927.English_Text: Did you see my power? Ha ha ha ha!
35000927.Chinese_Text: 你看到我的实力了吗？哈哈哈哈！
